Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright and \Nsit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:16.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:19.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:22.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who is there to support his mistress \Nin all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:24.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:28.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is about a boy who fights and puts \Nhis life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:32.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thank you for watching "Hayate \Nthe Combat Butler" again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us sing the theme song together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:45.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:45.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:52.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:52.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:55.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:55.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:04.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:04.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:07.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:07.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:13.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:13.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:16.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:16.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:23.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:23.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:29.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:29.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:32.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:32.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:36.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:36.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:41.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:41.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:48.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:48.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:55.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:55.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:10.98,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,245)}I Hear That Those Who Rule the \NSummer Rule at Entrance Exams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Miss Nishizawa's \Ndoing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:51.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One family sort of group...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:04.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Five to six customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two couples...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:31.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Full house...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anmitsu with ice cream, egg-drop \NNew Year's soup, tokoroten jelly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kudzu mochi, Abekawa mochi, \Nisobe-yaki rice cakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,country style zenzai, and a cream soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like all those things, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Hayate's doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:43.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it, I wonder what \NMiss Nishizawa was doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and take this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and lick her all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Miss Nishizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so glad! It {\i1}is{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:07.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the commotion with the \NMiss on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Miss Nishizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A delivery for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.18,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(221,197)}Hakuou Private Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.18,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(307,73)}Miss Nagi Sanzenin{middle}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:43.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, I feel bad about doing \Nthat to Miss Nishizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this to be good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:06:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So won't you please go out with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:06.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But right now, I have no business \Ngoing out with a girl anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm only interested \Nin 2-dimensional things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.85,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(488,112)}Crushed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There must have been a better \Nway to turn her down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:33.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have no idea what I should \Ndo in situations like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:37.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why did I think of \Nthe Miss right then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, a delivery has arrived for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks. Go ahead and open it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:07:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are technically a girl, \Nso please don't read like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:09.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet this is how it feels to be a big \Nbrother worried about his kid sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be a long time before I \Nhave time for a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:14.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have my hands full with the Miss already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks to be some documents \Nfrom Hakuou Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the transfer application, \Nright? For you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What do you mean, for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're documents for you \Nto transfer into Hakuou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I haven't heard about this.\N This is news to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm delivering the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I was dismissed from my old school!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I sent for documents \Nfrom that school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look. Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But what about the tuition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have those kind of financial means.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm paying for it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! What's the problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to go to school with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this is sort of \Nmy way of thanking you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:21.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll get to go back... to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss... Thank y...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What are you crying for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to make him cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! I didn't make him cry! \NHayate just started on his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to this document,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems you'll still have to \Ntake a transfer admission test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if he is to claim \Nto be a Sanzenin butler,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he had better be able to pass a mere \Ntransfer admission test from Hakuou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, Mr. Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't go killing \Nme off so thoughtlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, well... If he doesn't pass, \Nlet's just say he'll be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! After all this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't pass after everything \Nyou've done for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be inexcusable! \NAs a butler and as a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I shall put it on display for all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... My most earnest effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, Hakuou Academy requires \Na standard score of over 65.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, the transfer \Nadmission test is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A f-fart in a windstorm \Nis not necessary, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:46.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I wonder if Hayate \Nreally will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:49.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Considering his grades at his last school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:51.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's honestly going to be tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try not to let your \Nnerves get the better of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen to Maria's advice \Nand leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Head Butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wake up! Please \Nwake up! This is {\i1}my{\i0} bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not morning yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate Ayasaki, you misunderstand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, want you to be \Nadmitted to Hakuou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to pass tomorrow's \Ntransfer admission test!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do these eyes look like those of a liar's?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have my best interests at heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please leave and let me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have your best interests at heart
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's why I came to relate the \Nstory of my entrance exam experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being unreasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:43.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, really! This is not necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was back when I applied to enter \Na prestigious private kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, he's started already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a problem I just couldn't solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The end of the test period \Nwas fast approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, as young as I \Nwas, I could not solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just as my time was about to be up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus, you passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say that one \Nmustn't give up, no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head Butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My rare appearance has me feeling shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deluxe animation! Tama's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sine, cosine, tangent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The test's probably going to \Ncover some of that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama! How'd you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd tell you the \NHakuou entrance exam trends
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and teach you how to deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to learn anything from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate! Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not morning yet, so you've \Ngot plenty of time to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:05.89,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuou Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a little short on sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A streetcar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The campus is big, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did everything I could, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of test it's going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably pretty normal, \Nlike English and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:47.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think that study guide will \Nhelp you pass at all, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think Hakuou Academy's \Ntransfer admission test
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be something so normal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good of you to come, \Nex-suspicious individual!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Little Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your test administrator for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beautiful world history \Nteacher, Yukiji Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The b-beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't turn that into a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say it's not normal, Miss Katsura?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I took a normal test to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep looking back at the past
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll have nothing to gain \Nfrom the future, Little Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about the wisdom \Nof only looking ahead, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to begin the transfer \Nadmission test, so come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your assignment is none other than \Na Redmond-style interview exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Redmond-style interview exam refers to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:50.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a test that has been rapidly adopted \Nby businesses in recent years,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:53.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}which uses logic questions to test \Nthe true intelligence of applicants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:57.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Why are manhole covers round?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:16:00.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such tough brainteasers must \Nbe answered logically,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:02.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the test is used to judge \Nfundamental intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:05.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in a way that does not \Nrely on memorized facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Hakuou Academy's \Nprestige isn't for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even their transfer admission \Ntest is a bit different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why do you suppose \Nmanhole covers are round?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if it were square, the slightest \Nshift would cause it to fall in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the diagonal length of a \Nsquare is longer than its sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a circle, it's the same, \Neven if it shifts, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You're very smart, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not attending Hakuou \Non a whim or for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then we'll begin the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be taking place inside the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The test will begin the moment you enter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everything you say and do \Nwill be subject to scoring!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear that in mind in \Ntackling this challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, your first problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.41,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(166,20)}SNAP
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:17.65,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,CRAAAAASH
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mocking our Hayate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:28.09,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,134)}Can't show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you permitted to do whatever \Nyou please because you're a teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Nagi, your jabs are harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is the \Nprestigious Hakuou Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is a Redmond-style interview \Nexam to test your true intelligence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to give the answer that \Njust occurred to you, feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you really think \Nthat's the correct answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:49.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, it's true. \NBy the normal way of thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:52.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you use a tool to get the banana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's an intelligence test for monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:57.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, in Redmond-style interview exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:00.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the first answer that occurs \Nto you is usually wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:01.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In which case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key to this problem is none other than
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the height at which the banana is hung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The banana is actually at a height \Nthat you can reach by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the tools lying around \Nare all red herrings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The correct answer is none other than
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"grab it with your hand \Nwithout using any tools"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:44.07,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Growl~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:44.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkeys enduring hunger, \Nunable to cleverly reach the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The only food around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:51.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that was the catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means, after everything \NI went through,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:58.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's been a while, but I'm going \Nto get all bloody in this episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:02.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:05.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't win this fight, I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:10.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...get to go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't imagine he would choose \Nto fight instead of fleeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, this is animal abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your butler sure is putting up a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's got a lot riding \Non this test, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we cut the joke \Nshort and get on with the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! This was a joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. It'd be easy if you could \Ntest for intelligence like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you make me do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:20:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of wanted to loosen you up \Nas thanks for what you did for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need this sort of thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:08.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thus, in pretty poor condition, \Nboth mentally and physically,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hayate tackled the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:12.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I managed to answer all \Nthe questions somehow, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't pass after everything \Nyou've done for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall I do, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of discouraging \Ncomment is that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're certain to have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the promise in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go to school together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Madam Superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:21:02.04,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Superintendent's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm to deliver this notice \Nto the Sanzenin residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Madam Superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:11.11,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Not Accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps this is my imagination,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel like there is \None word too many here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he fell short of a \Npassing mark by one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he had taken the test \Nin a calmer frame of mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe he would have passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be counting on you \Nto do this, Miss Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the meantime, at the Sanzenin \Nresidence, not knowing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting ahead of ourselves, but \Nshall we celebrate your acceptance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Really?! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:50.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...they were already plunging \Ninto celebration mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:57.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If my dreams have taken your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:57.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Moshi boku no yume ga kimi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:02.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kizutsuke-tetara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:02.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And brought it pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:08.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sono omoi wa itsuka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:08.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:11.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boku ga morau yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:11.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take from you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:18.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Taisetsu na mono ni furue-nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:18.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While trembling over something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:24.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kakezuri-mawatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:24.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And madly dashing about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.02,0:22:29.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seou itami ni hibi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.02,0:22:29.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The hurt I bore made the days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:34.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muimi ni sugita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:34.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Go by emptily
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:39.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oikaketa mama de oikosare-tsuzuke
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:39.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just chasing and continually being overtaken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:44.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tohou ni kureru kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:44.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A wind who's lost its bearing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:49.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi no doko ni furetara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:49.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of you should I touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:55.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ii ka o sagashita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:55.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I sought it out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:23:00.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mamoritai yo kimi dake wa tsuyoku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:23:00.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You alone, I want to protect so much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:05.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yokubou no wadachi kara touzakatte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:05.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting away from the rut of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:10.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Itsuka subete te ni ireru sore ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:10.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, it will all be ours and that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:14.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi to boku no Proof
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:14.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is our proof, yours and mine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.17,0:23:25.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Namida mo zenbu azukeru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.17,0:23:25.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even all my tears, I entrust to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:27.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.45,0:23:28.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:30.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:30.68,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,240)}Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:33.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, did you have fun studying \Nfor the entrance exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.58,0:23:36.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it had been a while since I got \Nto enjoy feeling like a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:38.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:39.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks is not necessary, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:42.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to go to school \Ntogether every day now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:44.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Well, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.35,0:23:47.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be good-bye to days of \Nall-nighters and internet gaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:49.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:50.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:53.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! You're going to skip \Nschool with me from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:54.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:56.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:59.45,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,240)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.32,0:24:00.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a tiny prank! It \Nwas meant to be a little joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:19.47,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of "Hayate \Nthe Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.27,0:24:03.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined he would fall short \Nof passing by just one point!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:05.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you want me to come \Nwith you to apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.39,0:24:07.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if you please, that is \Nexactly what I am asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.27,0:24:10.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be holding a \Nmagnificent party today!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.02,0:24:12.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And we owe it all to that boy \Ngaining acceptance into Hakuou!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.04,0:24:15.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.86,0:24:19.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, hey! I hafta go to a party. \NHurry up, seriously".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.00,0:24:22.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,This situation makes bringing up the \Nsubject even harder than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.47,0:24:22.50,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! I hafta go to a party. \NHurry up, seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.26,0:24:24.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolute destiny: Apocalypse.
